  "description": "Six arms already active, sucker resonance prominent, the octopus alert and communicating. Mod wheel triggers the chromatophore cascade — at low wheel, skin patterns pulse slowly; at full throw, chromaDepth hits maximum and the arm modulation rate triples, the signal developing the alien vibrato signature of maximum chromatophore engagement. Each arm is an independent voice: at high wheel you hear all six shifting together in controlled chaos. Aftertouch deploys the ink defense: pressing into a sustained note raises inkMix and darkens the reverb tail, the sound retreating behind fluid opacity. Release the key and the ink disperses. Velocity shapes the sucker attack — light touch keeps the resonant click subtle; hard velocity brings the suckerMix forward immediately, the mechanical snap of muscular adhesion audible from the first millisecond.",
